<figureCitation box="[919,1069,1012,1047]" captionStart="Figs. 1 - 3" captionStartId="2.[651,722,2141,2172]" captionTargetBox="[180,1808,252,2056]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="Figs. 1 - 3.: (Lathys mussoriensis) sp. novo! i 1 1. Dorsal view (legs are omitted) 2. Epigyne 3. Internal genitalia" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3227110/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="44">Figs. 1-3</figureCitation>
